Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Return to the Womb of
    the Mother
  - 745
  - 208
By: Boehme
---
It is not enough to play the sophister： the grain of wheat brings
forth no fruit, unless it falls into the earth： all whatever will
bring forth fruit must enter into its mother from whence it came first
to be.
